OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779538270
OL,3,CFundraiser to help viral pug suffering
OL,4,Cfrom seizures tops #120,000
OL,6,FAn appeal to cover hospital treatment
OL,7,Ffor a dog that has a huge internet
OL,8,Ffollowing has raised more than
OL,9,F#120,000.
OL,11,FThe owners of Chilli the pug, from
OL,12,FLeeds, launched a crowdfunding appeal
OL,13,Fafter he was admitted for specialist
OL,14,Ftreatment at a neurology hospital
OL,15,Ffollowing a series of seizures.
OL,17,FIt has now become the biggest GoFundMe
OL,18,Fcampaign for an animal this year, with
OL,19,Fthousands of supporters donating.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
