FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779538270
OL,3,CFundraiser to help viral pug suffering
OL,4,Cfrom seizures tops #120,000
OL,6,FChilli's owners, social media
OL,7,Finfluencers Ollie and Helena Cutts,
OL,8,Fsay they asked for help because "our
OL,9,Fincome is not as predictable as people
OL,10,Fmight think".
OL,12,F"Social media income is irregular and
OL,13,Fmainly comes from brand deals, which
OL,14,Fwe do not do constantly," they said.
OL,16,F"We are not saying anyone has to pay
OL,17,Ffor Chilli. We would never want anyone
OL,18,Fto feel pressured.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779538270
OL,3,CFundraiser to help viral pug suffering
OL,4,Cfrom seizures tops #120,000
OL,6,F"We are simply asking that if Chilli
OL,7,Fhas made you, your friends, or your
OL,8,Ffamily smile over the years, and if
OL,9,Fyou are able and willing to help,
OL,10,Fdonating or sharing gives him a better
OL,11,Fchance."
OL,13,FChillli, who has more than one million
OL,14,Ffollowers on social media, was taken
OL,15,Fto an emergency vets after a major
OL,16,Fseizure.
OL,18,FHe was placed in an induced coma but
OL,19,Fhad a number of further episodes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
