CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779538270
OL,3,CFundraiser to help viral pug suffering
OL,4,Cfrom seizures tops #120,000
OL,6,FFollowing transfer to a specialist
OL,7,Fneurology hospital Chilli had further
OL,8,Ftreatment, including oxygen support,
OL,9,FMRI scans, specialist neurological
OL,10,Fcare, intensive monitoring, steroids
OL,11,Fand treatment for suspected brain
OL,12,Finflammation.
OL,14,FHis owners say the financial pressure
OL,15,Fhas been overwhelming, despite having
OL,16,Fpet insurance in place.
OL,18,FThey said: "Chilli is insured, because
OL,19,Fwe have always tried to do the
OL,20,Fresponsible thing for our dogs.
OL,26,@zD@LOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
