OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779538270
OL,3,CFundraiser to help viral pug suffering
OL,4,Cfrom seizures tops #120,000
OL,6,F"If his insurance claim is accepted,
OL,7,Fit will go towards the first emergency
OL,8,Fout of hours vet bill, but after that
OL,9,Fhis insurance is maxed out."
OL,11,FIn an update on Thursday, 21 May, they
OL,12,Fsaid Chilli's condition had improved
OL,13,Fand he was able to stand and was
OL,14,Feating, but added his stay in
OL,15,Fintensive care had been extended.
OL,17,FThey said: "After everything he has
OL,18,Fbeen through, every step forward feels
OL,19,Fenormous, but we know this is still a
OL,20,Fdelicate stage.
OL,26,@qD@\O]
